{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_05_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 一緒に食べようね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of commercial shooting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、表情が暗いぞ\nそんな顔じゃ、せっかくの可愛い衣装が台無しだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ you look gloomy.\nWith that face‚ your cute outfit will go to waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……\n今日のCM撮影、ちゃんと出来るのか不安で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry…\nI'm just worried if I can do well in today's commercial shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも台本は丸暗記してきましたから\n後は言われた通りにやればなんとかなりますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've memorized all the script‚ so\nIf I follow the instructions‚ it should be fine‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに台本通りにすれば無難にやり過ごせるだろう\nだが、さくらは本当にそれでいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you follow the script‚ it should be okay‚\nbut‚ Sakura‚ is that really enough for you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、さくらはどうして\n今回のCMに自分が抜擢されたと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you think you were chosen\nfor this commercial in the first place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7721931227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n今のサニピは人気急上昇中で勢いがあるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚\nSunny Peace is gaining popularity rapidly‚ and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それもあるだろうが、俺はさくらの魅力が\n新メニューの宣伝に向いていたからだと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be true‚ but I think you were chosen\nbecause your charm suits promoting the new menu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私が食べ物の宣伝に向いてるなんて……\n食レポも満足に出来ないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think I'm suitable for promoting food…?\nI can't even do food reporting properly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに上手とは言えないが、俺はさくらの食レポで\n一つだけ凄くいいところがあるのを見つけているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that you're not the best‚ but I've found one thing\nabout your food reports that's excellent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それは、とても美味しそうに食べることだ。その笑顔が\nどんな解説よりも雄弁に美味しさを伝えてくれるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the way you eat. Your smile conveys the taste\nmore vividly than any commentary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私の食べる姿が……私の笑顔が美味しさを伝える……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My way of eating… and my smile conveys the taste…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですよね\n暗い顔をしてたら美味しさは伝わらないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right. If I have a gloomy face‚\nthe taste won't come through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！　私らしく元気で明るい笑顔で\n美味しい気持ちを伝えてみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand! I'll be my cheerful self‚ with a bright smile‚\nand try to convey the tasty feeling!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "CMを見た人も笑顔になって\n一緒に食べたいって思ってもらえるように！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that people who see the commercial\nwill smile and want to eat together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "正確にやろうなんて考えなくていい\nさくららしく思いっきりぶつかってこい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't need to be too precise.\nBe yourself and go all out‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私らしく、笑顔で思いっきりやってみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'll be myself‚ and I'll give it my all with a bright smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "美味しい中華まんが食べたいな～\nそんな時は……じゃーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd love to have some great hot buns now.\nIn times like this… Ta-da!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "定番の中華まんが、さらに美味しくなって新登場！\n寒い冬はこれで決まりだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The classic hot bun is rolled out with upgraded taste!\nIt's perfect for the cold winter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（いいぞ、さくらの太陽のような明るさが）\n（伝わってくる眩しい笑顔だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Good‚ Sakura's bright and cheerful personality）\n（shines through with her dazzling smile.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "アツアツの中華まん、みんなで食べに来てね！\nいただきま～す！　ぱくっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Steaming hot buns! Come and eat with everyone!\nLet's dig in! Munch",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（あっ！　さくらのやつ、中華まんを食べ始めたぞ）\n（食べるなんて台本には無かったはずだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh! Sakura started eating the buns.）\n（Eating wasn't in the script though…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "はああぁ～、美味しい～！\n美味し過ぎてほっぺたゆるゆるです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ delicious!\nIt's so good that my cheeks are melting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、やっぱり美味しい物は\nみんなと一緒に食べたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ after all‚ delicious things\nare even more enjoyable when shared with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと一緒なら、もっともっと美味しくなるから……\n私と一緒に中華まん、食べようね♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm with everyone‚ it'll be much better…\nLet's eat hot buns together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらの台詞、後半はほとんどアドリブだな）\n（台本とはかなり違うが、この方がずっとさくららしい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura's lines in the latter part were mostly improvised.）\n（It's quite different from the script‚ but it's much more like Sakura.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
