      "text": "例のCM、かなり評判がいいらしいぞ\n見てると無性に中華まんを食べたくなると話題だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The recent commercial is getting a good response.\nPeople are talking about craving steamed buns when they see it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.900004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "話題になるのは嬉しいんですけど、複雑な気分です\nあの時は台本にないことを勝手にしちゃったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad that it's getting attention‚ but I get complicated about it.\nDuring that shoot‚ I did things off-script…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.0666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフのみなさんは「美味しそうに食べる笑顔が\n良かった」ってアドリブを褒めてくれましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The staff praised my improvisation of\neating with a smile‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.800004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それは本当に美味しかったから\n自然とああいう表情になっただけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was because it was genuinely great\nthat I naturally made that expression…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.7333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
