      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？\nでも、この前の食レポはうまく出来なかったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously!?\nBut I didn't do well in the last food report…",
